Cut! Cut! Cut!

573
00:47:39,109 --> 00:47:39,860
Props, what is this?!

574
00:47:39,902 --> 00:47:40,611
Sorry, Director.

575
00:47:40,652 --> 00:47:41,195
I'll get it fixed!

576
00:47:41,236 --> 00:47:41,987
What's with you?

577
00:47:42,029 --> 00:47:43,113
Is this intentional?

578
00:47:43,155 --> 00:47:44,364
Are you a real professional or not?

579
00:47:44,406 --> 00:47:45,199
